itl.enabler.api

Class TransactionCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • itl.enabler.api.TransactionCollection
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<Transaction>

    public class TransactionCollection
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<Transaction>
    A collection of Transaction objects

    Note : The collection of Transactions can be iterated with the foreach statement or accessed directly by its index.
    It can also be accessed by Transaction Id using the getById method.

    New transactions are pushed on to the front of the collection.

    See Also:
    Transaction
